ay you've hit your max spec bonus with items, the whole 1+level/5 thing. Does anyone know if rp bonuses will push you above this limit? It's fairly hard to test right now (you'd have to obtain quite a few +envenom items). I'm kinda looking for definitive answers, anyone can take a guess.<br>
<br>
thanks. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uczeris.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Czeris</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/6/02 12:32:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2040.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: RP spec bonuses and item spec bonuses</span><hr size=1> The cap is the same for RP bonuses and Item bonuses added together.  +11 at level 50.  Doesn't matter whether it's from items, or RPS, it's +11.  If they were separate, you could have up to +21 to skills, which is not going to happen. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ujaedenthestinker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jaeden The Stinker</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/6/02 12:52:07 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2040.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: RP spec bonuses and item spec bonuses</span><hr size=1> At level 43 i have 33 base envenom. I have 6 from items bringing it up to 39, and 1 from RPs. Bringing it to 40.  Thus letting me use the 40 dot. <p>~Jaeden The Stinker of Hibernia~</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uczeris.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Czeris</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/6/02 1:10:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2040.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: RP spec bonuses and item spec bonuses</span><hr size=1> Just to clarify...the bonuses *are* added together, but the share the same combined cap.  You could have +7 from items, and +4 from rps, or +3 from items and +8 from rps (in 200<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .  It's a max of +11 at level 50 for the combined bonuses. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usunthasbayne.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sunthas Bayne</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/6/02 3:31:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2040.topic&index=4>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: RP spec bonuses and item spec bonuses</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showMessage?topicID=1670.topic">pub35.ezboard.com/fthesaf...1670.topic</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
